data.description: LIKE NEW AND READY FOR YOU TO MOVE IN!!! 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths ranch home built in 2020 in desirable swim, playground, and trail community of Creekside in Monroe! Great location near Hwy 78! As you step into the home, you'll be greeted by an expansive open floor plan, perfect for hosting gatherings with family and friends. The kitchen is a highlight featuring modern stainless-steel appliances (refrigerator, range, microwave, dishwasher) large granite island, an eat-in kitchen area, walk in pantry, and granite counters too! The family room offers ample space for entertainment and relaxation. The split bedroom style provides privacy for everyone, making it the ideal layout for families or those who work from home. Your new home is situated on a beautiful, level lot. The covered patio offers the perfect spot for relaxing and taking in the peaceful surroundings. The inclusion of a one-year warranty by the homeowner is a nice touch, providing peace of mind for the new owner. Come and make this move-in-ready home yours! SOLD AS IS.
